data.meta_description: Braceface -  Canadian/Chinese animated series that aired on Teletoon in Canada, and on Disney Channel and ABC Family in the US, as well as Fox Kids. It is produced by American actress Alicia Silverstone, & made by the Canadian company Nelvana. The show, set in Elkford, British Columbia, recounts the travails of Sharon Spitz, who is a junior high school student with braces that get in the way of leading a normal teenage life.
